
Get the Client ID and secret in the link 

link/oauth/application


Create a new record in the Application Registry and provide the required details.

Authorize URL - https://dev186985.service-now.com/oauth/authorize
Token URL - https://dev186985.service-now.com/oauth/token
Redirect URL - https://dev186985.service-now.com/oauth_redirect.do
Default Grant Type - Authorization Code
Send Credentials - As Basic Authorization Header

Client ID and Client Secret will be provided from their end.
